item.title: S21E8: Devil Dogs of the Outback
item.description: In this episode, Kade interviews Mark, who shares his extraordinary experiences working in remote Australia. He also recounts being saved by traditional bush medicine after a spider bite and reflects on the psychological toll and PTSD resulting from his experiences...
